WorldStage Newsonline– John Holt Plc, a Nigerian conglomerate and subsidiary of John Holt & Co. (Liverpool) Ltd has released its unaudited 2020/2021 results quarter one October 2020 to December 2020 with 37.2% decline in revenue to N214 million from N341 million in same Q1 in 2019/2020. The company’s book remained in red during the quarter with the widening of loss by 326.7% to N367 million from N86 million loss in Q1 2019/2020.